[136.842801, "o", "──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mMost relevant to your current presentation work\u001b[51G\u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B-\u001b[5G\u001b[38;2;177;185;249m\u001b[1mknowledge/presenting-patterns-and-antipatterns-glossary-a-h\u001b[22m\u001b[39m (2026-07-14, 4515 tokens) — the patterns glossary you built for this talk\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[38;2;177;185;249m\u001b[1mknowledge/prezentare-16-iul-2026-cifre-externe-verificate\u001b[22m\u001b[39m (2026-07-11) — verified Sonnet 5 / GLM-5.2 figures + the \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mdetails/\u001b[39m pattern\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B-\u001b[5G\u001b[38;2;177;185;249m\u001b[1marchitecture/total-recall-plugin-architecture-and-gotchas\u001b[63G\u001b[22m\u001b[39m(imp=0.9)\u001b[73G—\u001b[75Gthe\u001b[79Gplugin\u001b[86Gdeep-dive,\u001b[97Gdirectly\u001b[106Gcite-able\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[38;2;177;185;249m\u001b[1mproject/deutsche-bank...flink-migration-design-(ollama-+-minimax)\u001b[71G\u001b[22m\u001b[39m+\u001b[73Gthe\u001b[77G\u001b[1mClaude Proposal\u001b[93G\u001b[22mtwin\u001b[98G(2026-07-03)\u001b[111G—\u001b[113Ga\u001b[115Greal\u001b[120GClaude-vs-Ollama\u001b[137Gside-by-side\u001b[150Gyou\u001b[154Gcan\u001b[158Gmine\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bfor\u001b[7Gthe\u001b[11Gcomparison\u001b[22Gslide\r\u001b[4C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;177;185;249m\u001b[1mtr\u001b[8Gubleshooting/\u001b[22Gotal-recall-semantic-search-rebuild-native-deps...\u001b[22m\u001b[39m (2026-07-16) — the sqlite-vec / better-sqlite3 native-addon saga\u001b[K\r\u001b[4C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;177;185;249m\u001b[1mrefer\u001b[11Gnc\u001b[15Ghow-to-do-a-presentation-softwar\u001b[48G-architecture-fundamentals\u001b[22m\u001b[39m — O'Re\u001b[82Glly sourc\u001b[92G for presentation craft\u001b[116G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mNotable: the bulk\u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B~440 of the 498 \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mknowledge\u001b[39m entries are the \u001b[1mFlink docs mirror\u001b[22m (Learn Flink, Table API,\u001b[88GSQL\u001b[92Gconcepts, etc., all 2026-07-09). Th\u001b[128Gt's noise\u001b[138Gfor\u001b[142Gthis\u001b[147Gpresentation\u001b[160Gbut\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bexplains the 568 count. If you want, I can \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mprune_memories\u001b[39m to surface low-retention\u001b[86GFlink-doc candida\u001b[104Ges — but only\u001b[118Gon\u001b[121Gyour\u001b[126Gsay-so.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[2BWant me to pull the\u001b[23Gfull\u001b[28Gbody\u001b[33Gof\u001b[36Gany\u001b[40Gspecific\u001b[49Gmemory\u001b[56G(e.g.\u001b[62Gthe\u001b[66Gverified-figures\u001b[83Gone,\u001b[88Gor\u001b[91Gthe\u001b[95GDeutsche\u001b[104GBank\u001b[109GClaude-vs-Ollama\u001b[126Gpair)\u001b[132Ginto\u001b[137Gcontext?\r\u001b[2B\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m✻\u001b[3GCrunched for 51s\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[48;2;55;55;55m\u001b[38;2;80;80;80m❯ \u001b[38;2;255;255;255mreview project from ../total-recall ; write conclusions in REVIEW-ollama-glm-5.2.txt\u001b[39m                                                                              \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[49m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m·\u001b[3G\u001b[38;2;235;159;127mSw\u001b[38;2;215;119;87mooping… \r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m  ⎿  Tip: Did you know you can drag and drop image files into your terminal?\r\u001b[3B❯ \u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[45;1H\u001b[42;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
