[255.99243, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3G-\u001b[5G\u001b[38;2;177;185;249m\u001b[1mtroubleshooting/total-recall-semantic-search-rebuild-native-deps...\u001b[73G\u001b[22m\u001b[39m(2026-07-16)\u001b[86G—\u001b[88Gthe\u001b[92Gsqlite-vec\u001b[103G/\u001b[105Gbetter-sqlite3\u001b[120Gnative-addon\u001b[133Gsaga\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[38;2;177;185;249m\u001b[1mreference/how-to-do-a-presentation-software-architecture-fundamentals\u001b[75G\u001b[22m\u001b[39m—\u001b[77GO'Reilly\u001b[86Gsource\u001b[93Gfor\u001b[97Gpresentation\u001b[110Gcraft\r\u001b[2C\u001b[2B\u001b[1mNotable: the bulk\u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B~440\u001b[8Gof\u001b[11Gthe\u001b[15G498\u001b[19G\u001b[38;2;177;185;249mknowledge\u001b[29G\u001b[39mentries\u001b[37Gare\u001b[41Gthe\u001b[45G\u001b[1mFlink docs mirror\u001b[63G\u001b[22m(Learn\u001b[70GFlink,\u001b[77GTable\u001b[83GAPI,\u001b[88GSQL\u001b[92Gconcepts,\u001b[102Getc.,\u001b[108Gall\u001b[112G2026-07-09).\u001b[125GThat's\u001b[132Gnoise\u001b[138Gfor\u001b[142Gthis\u001b[147Gpresentation\u001b[160Gbut\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bexplains the 568 count. If you want,\u001b[40GI can \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mprune_memories\u001b[39m to surface low-retenti\u001b[85G Flink-doc candidates —\u001b[109Gbut only on your\u001b[126Gs\u001b[128Gy-so.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2B \u001b[3GWant me to pull the\u001b[23Gfull\u001b[28Gbody\u001b[33Gof\u001b[36Gany\u001b[40Gspecific\u001b[49Gmemory\u001b[56G(e.g.\u001b[62Gthe\u001b[66Gverified-figures\u001b[83Gone,\u001b[88Gor\u001b[91Gthe\u001b[95GDeutsche\u001b[104GBank\u001b[109GClaude-vs-Ollama\u001b[126Gpair)\u001b[132Ginto\u001b[137Gcontext?\r\u001b[2B\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m✻\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;153;153;153mCrunched for 51s\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2B\u001b[48;2;55;55;55m\u001b[38;2;80;80;80m❯ \u001b[38;2;255;255;255mreview project from ../total-recall ; write conclusions in REVIEW-ollama-glm-5.2.txt\u001b[39m                                                                              \r\u001b[2B\u001b[49m \u001b[3G\u001b[38;2;153;153;153mThought for \u001b[1m17s\u001b[22m \u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;255;255;255m●\u001b[3G\u001b[39mI'll\u001b[8Greview\u001b[15Gthe\u001b[19Gtotal-recall\u001b[32Gproject\u001b[40Gand\u001b[44Gwrite\u001b[50Gconclusions.\u001b[63GLet\u001b[67Gme\u001b[70Gfirst\u001b[76Gorient:\u001b[84Gpull\u001b[89Gthe\u001b[93Garchitecture\u001b[106Gmemory\u001b[113GI\u001b[115Galready\u001b[123Ghave\u001b[128Gindexed,\u001b[137Gand\u001b[141Gscout\u001b[147Gthe\u001b[151Grepo\u001b[156Gstructure\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bin parallel.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2B \u001b[3G\u001b[38;2;153;153;153mThought for \u001b[1m35s\u001b[22m, called plugin:total-recall:total-recall, ran \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m shell command \u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;255;255;255m●\u001b[3G\u001b[39mGood context.\u001b[17GThe\u001b[21Grepo\u001b[26Ghas\u001b[30G\u001b[38;2;177;185;249mollama-minimax-proposals.md\u001b[39m,\u001b[59G\u001b[38;2;177;185;249mollama-gdm-proposals.md\u001b[39m,\u001b[84G\u001b[38;2;177;185;249mfable-proposals.md\u001b[39m,\u001b[104Gplus\u001b[109Gthe\u001b[113Gplugin\u001b[120Gitself\u001b[127Gunder\u001b[133G\u001b[38;2;177;185;249mplugins/total-recall/\u001b[39m.\u001b[156GThe\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Boutput\u001b[10Gfilename\u001b[19G\u001b[38;2;177;185;249mREVIEW-ollama-glm-5.2.txt\u001b[45G\u001b[39msignals\u001b[53Gthe\u001b[57Gangle:\u001b[64Gthe\u001b[68GOllama\u001b[75Gintegration\u001b[87G+\u001b[89GGLM-5.2\u001b[97G(the\u001b[102Gcloud\u001b[108Gmodel\u001b[114Grunning\u001b[122Gthis\u001b[127Gsession).\u001b[137GLet\u001b[141Gme\u001b[144Gscout\u001b[150Gdeeper\u001b[157Gbefore\r\u001b[1B \u001b[3Gfan\u001b[7Ging out.\u001b[16G\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m●\u001b[3G\u001b[39mThinking for \u001b[1m52s\u001b[22m, running \u001b[1m1\u001b[31G\u001b[22mshell\u001b[37Gcommand…\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m  ⎿  \u001b[39m\u001b[2m\u001b[3mNow I have a strong scout. Let me note the key facts: - The repo already has prior reviews: \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mARCHITECTURE-REVIEW-TODO.md\u001b[39m (8 items), \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mfable-proposals.md\u001b[39m (Fable \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1Breview), \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mollama-minimax-proposals.md\u001b[39m, \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mollama-gdm-proposals.md\u001b[39m. So previous models (Fable, and presumably others) have reviewed this. The user now wants a \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1Breview from GLM-5.2 (the current cloud model) — written to \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mREVIEW-ollama-glm-5.2.txt\u001b[39m. The \"ollama\" in the filename signals the angle: focus on the Ollama \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1Bintegration (embeddings) and the cloud-vs-local theme. - The total-recall plugin uses Ollama for embeddings (via \u001b[38;2;177;185;249membeddings.ts\u001b[39m), with sqlite-vec + \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1Bbetter-sqlite3 + @huggingface/transformers as optional deps. Vector search is currently OFF because Ollama embedding is failing (the aborted operations I saw \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1Bin get_stats). - The presentation is \"Claude vs Ollama\" + total-recall. So a review from GLM-5.2 (a cloud model, the one running this session) of a project \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1Bthat integrates Ollama (local model) is thematically perfect. I have enough to fan out a workflow. The work-l"]
[255.992772, "o", "ist (review dimensions): 1. Ollama embedding \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1Bintegration — \u001b[38;2;177;185;249membeddings.ts\u001b[39m, \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mvectorStore.ts\u001b[39m, the timeout/retry (commit 7c204d9), the failure mode currently active. This is the core \"ollama\" angle. 2. Core \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1Barchitecture & code quality — \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mserver.ts\u001b[39m, \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mtools/*\u001b[39m, \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mstate.ts\u001b[39m, \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mpersistence.ts\u001b[39m, \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mtfidf.ts\u001b[39m, \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mrrf.ts\u001b[39m, \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mebbinghaus.ts\u001b[39m. The 8-item ARCHITECTURE-REVIEW-TODO + \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1Bfable-proposals already exist — I should build on/critique them, not duplicate. 3. Install/distribution — \u001b[38;2;177;185;249minstall.sh\u001b[39m (42KB!),…\r\u001b[38C\u001b[2B\u001b[23m\u001b[22m\u001b[38;2;153;153;153mthought for 48s)\u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[45;1H\u001b[42;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
