[371.959142, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;255;255;255m●\u001b[39m Good context. The repo has \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mollama-minimax-proposals.md\u001b[39m, \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mollama-gdm-proposals.md\u001b[39m, \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mfable-proposals.md\u001b[39m, plus the plugin itself under \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mplugins/total-recall/\u001b[39m. The\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Boutput\u001b[10Gfilename\u001b[19G\u001b[38;2;177;185;249mREVIEW-ollama-glm-5.2.txt\u001b[45G\u001b[39msignals\u001b[53Gthe\u001b[57Gangle:\u001b[64Gthe\u001b[68GOllama\u001b[75Gintegration\u001b[87G+\u001b[89GGLM-5.2\u001b[97G(the\u001b[102Gcloud\u001b[108Gmodel\u001b[114Grunning\u001b[122Gthis\u001b[127Gsession).\u001b[137GLet\u001b[141Gme\u001b[144Gscout\u001b[150Gdeeper\u001b[157Gbefore\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bfanning out.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2B \u001b[3G\u001b[38;2;153;153;153mThought for \u001b[1m52s\u001b[22m, ran \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m shell command \u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;255;255;255m●\u001b[3G\u001b[39mStrong\u001b[10Gscout\u001b[16Gcomplete.\u001b[26GThe\u001b[30Grepo\u001b[35Galready\u001b[43Ghas\u001b[47Gprior\u001b[53Gcloud-model\u001b[65Greviews\u001b[73G(\u001b[38;2;177;185;249mfable-proposals.md\u001b[39m,\u001b[94G\u001b[38;2;177;185;249mollama-minimax-proposals.md\u001b[39m,\u001b[123G\u001b[38;2;177;185;249mollama-gdm-proposals.md\u001b[39m)\u001b[148Gplus\u001b[153Gan\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;177;185;249mARCHITECTURE-REVIEW-TODO.md\u001b[39m with 8 items. So GLM-5.2's review should (a) focus\u001b[82Gon\u001b[85Gthe\u001b[89G\u001b[1mOllama embedding integration\u001b[118G\u001b[22m(the\u001b[123Glive\u001b[128Gfailure\u001b[136GI\u001b[138Gsaw\u001b[142G—\u001b[144Gvector\u001b[151Gsearch\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsilently\u001b[12Goff\u001b[16G—\u001b[18Gis\u001b[21Gthe\u001b[25Gheadline),\u001b[36Gand\u001b[40G(b)\u001b[44Gbuild\u001b[50Gon\u001b[53G/\u001b[55Gdelta\u001b[61Gagainst\u001b[69Gthe\u001b[73Gprior\u001b[79Greviews\u001b[87Grather\u001b[94Gthan\u001b[99Gduplicate\u001b[109Gthem.\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BI'll fan out a review workflow: 9 dimensions → adversaria\u001b[61G verification\u001b[75Gof \u001b[79Gach actionable finding\u001b[102G→ I author the f\u001b[120Gal \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mREVIEW-ollama-glm-5.2.txt\u001b[39m from the\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bco\u001b[6Gf\u001b[8Grmed evidence.\r\u001b[2B\u001b[38;2;78;186;101m●\u001b[3G\u001b[39m\u001b[1mWorkflow\u001b[22m(GLM-5.2 review of the total-recall\u001b[47Gplugin,\u001b[55GOllama-integration\u001b[74Gangle,\u001b[81Gwith\u001b[86Gadversarial\u001b[98Gverification)\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m  ⎿  Running in background · \u001b[38;2;177;185;249m/workflows\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m to monitor and save\r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;153;153;153mThought for \u001b[1m21s\u001b[22m \u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;255;255;255m●\u001b[3G\u001b[39mWorkflow\u001b[12Gis\u001b[15Grunning\u001b[23Gin\u001b[26Gthe\u001b[30Gbackground\u001b[41G(9\u001b[44Greviewers\u001b[54G→\u001b[56Gadversarial\u001b[68Gverifiers).\u001b[80GWhile\u001b[86Git\u001b[89Gruns,\u001b[95GI'll\u001b[100Gindependently\u001b[114Gground\u001b[121Gmyself\u001b[128Gin\u001b[131Gthe\u001b[135GOllama-critical\u001b[151Gfiles\u001b[157Gso\u001b[160GI\u001b[162Gcan\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsanity-check\u001b[16Gthe ag\u001b[23Gnts' findings\u001b[38Guri\u001b[42Gg synthesis.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m \u001b[3G\u001b[39mThinking\u001b[12Gfor\u001b[16G\u001b[1m46s\u001b[22m,\u001b[21Greading\u001b[29G\u001b[1m2\u001b[31G\u001b[22mfiles…\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m  ⎿  \u001b[39m\u001b[2m\u001b[3mGood, I now have grounded understanding of the Ollama embedding path. Key observations I can already see: 1. Ollama model default is \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mbge-m3\u001b[39m (line 68), endpoint\r\u001b[1B\u001b[23m\u001b[22m     \u001b[38;2;177;185;249m\u001b[2m\u001b[3mhttp://127.0.0.1:11434/api/embeddings\u001b[39m. Timeout 10s, one retry with 200ms backoff. The code is well-commented and thoughtful. 2. Silent degradation: when \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1BOllama fails, \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mgetExternalEmbedding\u001b[39m returns null → \u001b[38;2;177;185;249membed()\u001b[39m returns null → recall degrades to TF-IDF. The error IS recorded via \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mrecordError\u001b[39m (line 84) and \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[23m\u001b[22m   \u001b[2m\u001b[3msurfaced in \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mget_stats.recentErrors\u001b[39m. So it's not fully silent — it's observable via get_stats. But the user only sees it if they call get_stats. There's no \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1BSessionStart banner saying \"vector search unavailable.\" This matches the live state I saw (vectorSearchEnabled:false, 10 aborted errors). 3. \r\u001b[1B\u001b[23m\u001b[22m \u001b[3G   \u001b[38;2;177;185;249m\u001b[2m\u001b[3misVectorAvailable()\u001b[39m (line 182): for Ollama (non-huggingface provider), returns \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mexternalEmbedSuccess\u001b[39m which is only true after a successful embed. So get_stats \u001b[23m\u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B   \u001b[2m\u001b[3mhonestly reports false until a successful embed. Good — no false advertising. 4. Embedding dimension: \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mensureVecTable\u001b[39m creates the tabl"]
[371.959484, "o", "e lazily with the incoming\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1Bvector's dimension, and drops/recreates if dimension or metric changes. So dimension mismatch is handled by dropping the table (data loss for vectors, but \r\u001b[1B\u001b[23m\u001b[22m \u001b[3G   \u001b[2m\u001b[3mthey get backfilled by reconcileIndex). Reasonable. 5. \u001b[38;2;177;185;249msearchVector\u001b[39m returns \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mscore: 1 - r.distance\u001b[39m (line 89) — for cosine distance in sqlite-vec, distance = 1 -\r\u001b[1B\u001b[23m\u001b[22m     \u001b[2m\u001b[3mcosine_similarity, so score = cosine_similarity. Good. 6. The fire-and-forget embedAndUpsert + flushEmbeddings on…\r\u001b[46C\u001b[2B\u001b[23m\u001b[22m\u001b[38;2;153;153;153mthought for 24s)\u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[45;1H\u001b[39;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
