Gclean\u001b[70GJSON.\u001b[76GLet\u001b[80Gme\u001b[83Ginspect\u001b[91Gits\u001b[95Gactual\u001b[102Gshape.\r\u001b[2B \u001b[3G\u001b[38;2;153;153;153mThought for \u001b[1m5s\u001b[22m, ran \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m shell command \u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2B\u001b[38;2;255;255;255m●\u001b[3G\u001b[39mThe JSON is wrapped under \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mresult\u001b[39m — my\u001b[41Gscript\u001b[48Gqueried\u001b[56Gthe\u001b[60Gwrong\u001b[66Glevel.\u001b[73GLet\u001b[77Gme\u001b[80Gfix.\r\u001b[2B \u001b[3G\u001b[38;2;153;153;153mThought for \u001b[1m2s\u001b[22m, ran \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m shell command \u001b[40G\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2B\u001b[38;2;255;255;255m●\u001b[3G\u001b[39mNow the confirmed\u001b[21G+ partial\u001b[33Gndings in detail, so I c\u001b[59G author\u001b[67Gthe\u001b[71Greview.\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;153;153;153mThought for \u001b[1m11s\u001b[22m, read \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file, ran \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m shell command \u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m  ⎿  Read \u001b[1m../CLAUDE.md\u001b[22m (45 lines)\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m  ⎿  Read \u001b[1m../../CLAUDE.md\u001b[22m (40 lines)\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[13C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m\u001b[1mtotal-recall/plugins/total-recall/src/embeddings.ts\u001b[22m (198 lines)\r\u001b[13C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mtotal-recall/plugins/total-recall/src/vectorStore.ts\u001b[22m (124 lines)\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1BS\u001b[8GssionStart:compact says: dash0: telemetry is not active —\u001b[66Gconfigur\u001b[75G the plugin to start sending data. Run /plugin → Installed → dash0 → Configure, then \r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m     \u001b[38;2;153;153;153m/reload-plugins.\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;255;255;255m●\u001b[3G\u001b[39mI\u001b[5Ghave the full findings\u001b[28Gset.\u001b[33GWriting\u001b[41Gthe\u001b[45Greview\u001b[52Gnow.\u001b[45;1H\u001b[42;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
