ories\u001b[39m — and on the \u001b[3mread path\u001b[23m via \u001b[38;2;177;185;249msearchVector\u001b[39m. Plus \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mrerank_memories\u001b[39m \u001b[86G-embedding every candidate every call.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1m§2–§8\u001b[22m — core sea\u001b[22Gch (TF-IDF substring boost, no length norm), server/state (deprecated \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mServer\u001b[39m \u001b[100Glass, no boundary validati\u001b[127Gn\u001b[130G\u001b[38;2;177;185;249mconfirm_memory\u001b[39m treats\u001b[152G\u001b[38;2;177;185;249m'no'\u001b[157G\u001b[39mas\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bconfirmation, error-text regex in import), per\u001b[50Gistence (\u001b[60Go flock, no fsync, fallback loses atomicity, full\u001b[110Gvault walk on boot, BOM not stripped, no\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BschemaVersion), install/hooks (standalone omits SessionEnd, plugin.json missing\u001b[83Gthe \u001b[38;2;177;185;249mhooks\u001b[39m field install.\u001b[108Gh claims\u001b[117GCopilot reads, no\u001b[135Ghook-level dedup, timeout\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bfield-n\u001b[11Gme\u001b[14Gdivergence), p\u001b[29Giv\u001b[32Gcy/org-sync (secret filte\u001b[58G prefix-\u001b[68Gly, PII f\u001b[79Gter email-only, sync failures exit 0, queue job deleted\u001b[135Gbefore\u001b[142Gsync),\u001b[149Gtests\u001b[155G(untested\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BEbbinghaus\u001b[14Gguards,\u001b[22Gtwo partials), docs parity (stale presenta\u001b[65Gion URL, Copilot \"in progress\"\u001b[96Gvs \u001b[100Gmplemented, b\u001b[114Goken Codex anchor).\u001b[K"]
